---
layout: base.njk
title: Oikos – Bouwend Bureau | Den Haag
description: Duurzame renovatie met hennepvezels. Guido Bouwman maakt woningen klaar voor 2050.
---

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section id="home" class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col overflow-hidden" data-nav-bg="transparent" data-nav-theme="light">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div class="hero-slides absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/assets/img/oikos-10.jpg" alt="Oikos project" class="hero-slide active" />
      <img src="/assets/img/oikos-1.jpg" alt="Oikos project" class="hero-slide" />
      <img src="/assets/img/oikos-3.jpg" alt="Oikos project" class="hero-slide" />
      <img src="/assets/img/oikos-20.jpg" alt="Oikos project" class="hero-slide" />
      <img src="/assets/img/oikos-6.jpg" alt="Oikos project" class="hero-slide" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-overlay absolute inset-0"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Gecentreerde naam + tekst -->
  <div class="relative z-10 flex-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="hero-label text-oikos-green font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-xs mb-6">
        Den Haag &nbsp;·&nbsp; Duurzame renovatie
      </p>
      <img src="/assets/img/logo-tekst.png" alt="Oikos Bouwend Bureau" class="h-16 sm:h-24 md:h-32 w-auto mx-auto drop-shadow-md" />
      <p class="hero-p text-white/85 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-xl mx-auto mt-10 font-light leading-relaxed min-h-[2em]">
        <span id="hero-typewriter"></span><span class="typewriter-cursor">|</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Stats onderaan hero, zichtbaar op alle schermen -->
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full hero-right">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-6 md:pb-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-2 md:gap-3">
        <div class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur border border-white/10 rounded-2xl px-3 py-4 sm:px-5 sm:py-5 text-center flex flex-col justify-between">
          <p class="text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest h-4 flex items-center justify-center mb-1">Tot</p>
          <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">90%</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-[10px] sm:text-xs uppercase tracking-widest leading-snug">Energiebesparing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur border border-white/10 rounded-2xl px-3 py-4 sm:px-5 sm:py-5 text-center flex flex-col justify-between">
          <p class="text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest h-4 flex items-center justify-center mb-1">&nbsp;</p>
          <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-oikos-green mb-2">CO₂−</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-[10px] sm:text-xs uppercase tracking-widest leading-snug">Negatief materiaal</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur border border-white/10 rounded-2xl px-3 py-4 sm:px-5 sm:py-5 text-center flex flex-col justify-between">
          <p class="text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest h-4 flex items-center justify-center mb-1">Streven naar</p>
          <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">0%</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-[10px] sm:text-xs uppercase tracking-widest leading-snug">Formaldehyde</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur border border-white/10 rounded-2xl px-3 py-4 sm:px-5 sm:py-5 text-center flex flex-col justify-between">
          <p class="text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest h-4 flex items-center justify-center mb-1">&nbsp;</p>
          <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">16u</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-[10px] sm:text-xs uppercase tracking-widest leading-snug">Thermische fase&shy;verschuiving</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<!-- ===== DIENSTEN STRIP ===== -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white border-b border-gray-100" data-nav-bg="#ffffff" data-nav-theme="dark">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 fade-up">
      <span class="section-tag">Wat doet Oikos?</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark">Bouwkundig ontwerp én uitvoering,<br>van eerste schets tot opgeleverd resultaat.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <div class="border-t-2 border-oikos-green pt-6 fade-up d1">
        <span class="text-oikos-green font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 block">01</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-oikos-dark mb-3 text-lg">Bouwkundigen die zelf bouwen</h3>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Oikos ontwerpt en voert zelf uit. Geen tussenpersonen, geen aannemers. Dat betekent korte lijnen, directe communicatie en vakwerk van begin tot eind.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t-2 border-oikos-green pt-6 fade-up d2">
        <span class="text-oikos-green font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 block">02</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-oikos-dark mb-3 text-lg">Woningen energiezuinig maken</h3>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Oikos werkt aan één doel: de woning meetbaar energiezuiniger maken. Geen losse maatregelen, maar een samenhangende aanpak van het hele gebouw, van analyse tot meting achteraf.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t-2 border-oikos-green pt-6 fade-up d3">
        <span class="text-oikos-green font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 block">03</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-oikos-dark mb-3 text-lg">Circulaire, natuurlijke materialen</h3>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Oikos werkt met biobased en circulaire materialen. Gezond voor de bewoner, goed voor het klimaat en volledig afbreekbaar. Dat is geen marketingverhaal, maar een bewuste keuze bij elk project.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== PROJECTEN & NIEUWS ===== -->
<section id="projecten" class="py-16 md:py-28 bg-white" data-nav-bg="#ffffff" data-nav-theme="dark">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-end justify-between gap-4 mb-10 md:mb-16">
      <div class="fade-up">
        <span class="section-tag">Projecten & nieuws</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark leading-tight">
          Wat we doen,<br>schrijven we op.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/nieuws/" class="text-oikos-green hover:text-oikos-green-dark font-semibold text-sm flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors">
        Alle berichten
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    {%- set allPosts = collections.post | reverse -%}

    {% if allPosts.length > 0 %}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {% for post in allPosts %}
        {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
        <article class="card-hover group fade-up d{{ loop.index }} rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="block">
            <div class="overflow-hidden aspect-video bg-oikos-green-light">
              {% if post.data.image %}
              <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" />
              {% else %}
              <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <img src="/assets/logo-hart.png" alt="Oikos" class="h-14 opacity-20" />
              </div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="h-0.5 bg-oikos-green origin-left scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
            <div class="p-5">
              <p class="text-oikos-gray text-xs mb-3">{{ post.date | dutchDate }}</p>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-oikos-dark group-hover:text-oikos-green transition-colors leading-snug mb-2">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
              <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-2">{{ post.data.excerpt or post.templateContent | striptags | truncate(120) }}</p>
              <p class="text-oikos-green text-sm font-semibold mt-4 flex items-center gap-1 opacity-0 translate-y-2 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-300">
                Lees meer
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="text-center py-20 border-2 border-dashed border-oikos-green-light rounded-2xl">
      <img src="/assets/logo-hart.png" alt="Oikos" class="h-12 opacity-20 mx-auto mb-4" />
      <p class="text-oikos-gray mb-4">Er zijn nog geen berichten.</p>
      <a href="/admin/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-oikos-green text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-oikos-green-dark transition-colors">
        + Eerste bericht toevoegen
      </a>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== MATERIAAL – HENNEPVEZELS ===== -->
<section id="materiaal" class="py-16 md:py-28 bg-oikos-dark overflow-hidden" data-nav-bg="#3C3C3C" data-nav-theme="light">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6 mb-12 fade-up">
      <div>
        <span class="text-oikos-green text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3 block">Biobased materialen</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
          Gebouwd van<br>wat de aarde geeft.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/materialen/" class="text-oikos-green hover:text-white font-semibold text-sm flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors flex-shrink-0">
        Volledige kennisbank
        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 fade-up d1">

      <a href="/materialen/?m=hennep" class="mat-home-card group">
        <span class="mat-home-tag">Kalkhennep</span>
        <h3 class="mat-home-title">EXIE CaNaDry</h3>
        <p class="mat-home-desc">CO₂-negatief, dampdoorlatend en volledig biobased. Het meest compacte isolatiepakket voor bestaande woningen.</p>
        <div class="mat-home-stat">
          <span class="mat-home-stat-val">0,054</span>
          <span class="mat-home-stat-unit">W/mK</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mat-home-arrow">→</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/materialen/?m=schapenwol" class="mat-home-card group">
        <span class="mat-home-tag">Dierlijk biobased</span>
        <h3 class="mat-home-title">Schapenwol</h3>
        <p class="mat-home-desc">Neemt tot 35% van het eigen gewicht aan vocht op zonder isolatiewaarde te verliezen. Zelfblussend en biologisch afbreekbaar.</p>
        <div class="mat-home-stat">
          <span class="mat-home-stat-val">0,035</span>
          <span class="mat-home-stat-unit">W/mK</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mat-home-arrow">→</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/materialen/?m=cellulose" class="mat-home-card group">
        <span class="mat-home-tag">Gerecycled papier</span>
        <h3 class="mat-home-title">Cellulose</h3>
        <p class="mat-home-desc">Inblaasisolatie van gerecycled krantenpapier. Geschikt voor renovaties zonder openbreken van de constructie.</p>
        <div class="mat-home-stat">
          <span class="mat-home-stat-val">0,038</span>
          <span class="mat-home-stat-unit">W/mK</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mat-home-arrow">→</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/materialen/?m=houtvezel" class="mat-home-card group">
        <span class="mat-home-tag">Biobased hout</span>
        <h3 class="mat-home-title">Houtvezel</h3>
        <p class="mat-home-desc">Hoge thermische massa beschermt tegen oververhitting in de zomer. Beschikbaar als plaat, mat of inblaasmateriaal.</p>
        <div class="mat-home-stat">
          <span class="mat-home-stat-val">8–12u</span>
          <span class="mat-home-stat-unit">faseverschuiving</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mat-home-arrow">→</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/materialen/?m=isovlas" class="mat-home-card group">
        <span class="mat-home-tag">Plantvezels</span>
        <h3 class="mat-home-title">Isovlas</h3>
        <p class="mat-home-desc">Gemaakt van lijnvezels, geteeld in de Lage Landen. Lage grijze energie, goede vochtregulering en makkelijk verwerken.</p>
        <div class="mat-home-stat">
          <span class="mat-home-stat-val">0,035</span>
          <span class="mat-home-stat-unit">W/mK</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mat-home-arrow">→</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/materialen/" class="mat-home-card mat-home-cta group flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center">
        <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-oikos-green mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/></svg>
        <p class="text-oikos-dark font-bold text-sm">Volledige kennisbank</p>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-xs mt-1">Specs, tekeningen en meer</p>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mat-home-card {
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid #e8f0d8;
    background: #ffffff;
    transition: border-color 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s, transform 0.25s;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .mat-home-card:hover {
    border-color: #8DC63F;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(141,198,63,0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .mat-home-cta {
    border-style: dashed;
    border-color: #c8dfa8;
    background: #EFF7DC;
    min-height: 160px;
  }
  .mat-home-cta:hover {
    background: #e2f0c4;
    border-color: #8DC63F;
  }
  .mat-home-tag  { font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #8DC63F; display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .mat-home-title{ font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 800; color: #3C3C3C; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .mat-home-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #6B6B6B; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .mat-home-stat { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 4px; }
  .mat-home-stat-val  { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: #3C3C3C; font-family: monospace; }
  .mat-home-stat-unit { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #9B9B9B; }
  .mat-home-arrow { position: absolute; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; color: rgba(141,198,63,0); font-size: 1.1rem; transition: color 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
  .mat-home-card:hover .mat-home-arrow { color: #8DC63F; transform: translateX(3px); }
  .mat-home-cta .text-white { color: #3C3C3C !important; }
  .mat-home-cta .text-white\/40 { color: #6B6B6B !important; }
</style>

<!-- ===== OVER OIKOS ===== -->
<section id="over-ons" class="py-16 md:py-28 bg-oikos-green-light" data-nav-bg="#EFF7DC" data-nav-theme="dark">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">

      <div class="fade-up">
        <span class="section-tag">Wie we zijn</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark mb-6 leading-tight">
          Guido Bouwman —<br>specialist in biobased<br>renovatie.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Oikos is opgericht door Guido Bouwman vanuit een heldere overtuiging: duurzame renovatie moet meetbaar zijn en écht werken. Hij combineert ambachtelijk vakmanschap met kennis van biobased materialen.
        </p>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Elk pand is anders. Guido kijkt zelf naar de situatie en stelt een aanpak op maat voor — van eerste gesprek tot oplevering. Kleine teams, korte lijnen, één aanspreekpunt.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <img src="/assets/img/logo-hart-transparant.png" alt="Oikos" class="h-12" />
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-oikos-dark">Guido Bouwman</p>
            <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm">Oprichter · Oikos Bouwend Bureau · Den Haag</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl fade-up d1">
        <img src="/assets/img/guido.png" alt="Guido Bouwman aan het werk" class="w-full object-cover aspect-[4/3]" />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== WERKWIJZE ===== -->
<section id="diensten" class="py-16 md:py-28 bg-white" data-nav-bg="#ffffff" data-nav-theme="dark">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

    <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-20 fade-up">
      <span class="section-tag">Hoe we werken</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark">Van eerste gesprek<br>tot opgeleverd werk.</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Mobiel: 2 kolommen compacte kaartjes -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 md:hidden">
      {% set stappen = [
        { nr: "01", titel: "Intake & analyse", tekst: "Constructie, gebruik en ambities in kaart." },
        { nr: "02", titel: "Materiaalplan", tekst: "Plan op maat: dikte, detaillering, aansluiting." },
        { nr: "03", titel: "Uitvoering", tekst: "Kleine teams, nauwkeurig werk, korte lijnen." },
        { nr: "04", titel: "Oplevering", tekst: "Meting van het resultaat na oplevering." }
      ] %}
      {% for stap in stappen %}
      <div class="bg-oikos-green-light rounded-2xl p-4">
        <span class="text-oikos-green font-extrabold text-xs block mb-2">{{ stap.nr }}</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-oikos-dark text-sm mb-1">{{ stap.titel }}</h3>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-xs leading-relaxed">{{ stap.tekst }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <!-- Desktop: 4 kolommen met animerende lijn -->
    <div class="hidden md:grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 relative">
      <div class="absolute top-8 left-[12.5%] right-[12.5%] h-0.5 bg-gray-100 z-0"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-8 left-[12.5%] right-[12.5%] h-0.5 bg-oikos-green z-0 line-loop"></div>

      {% set stappen = [
        { nr: "01", titel: "Intake & analyse", tekst: "We kijken naar de constructie, het gebruik en de ambities. Geen standaard offerte — maar een reëel advies op maat." },
        { nr: "02", titel: "Materiaalplan", tekst: "Op basis van de analyse stellen we een plan op. Welke dikte, welke detaillering, hoe aansluitend op bestaand werk." },
        { nr: "03", titel: "Uitvoering", tekst: "Kleine teams, nauwkeurig werk. Heldere communicatie over voortgang en eventuele afwijkingen van het plan." },
        { nr: "04", titel: "Oplevering & meting", tekst: "Na oplevering meten we het resultaat. Blower door test voor luchtdichtheid, thermische inspectie op verzoek." }
      ] %}

      {% for stap in stappen %}
      <div class="text-center relative z-10 fade-up d{{ loop.index }}">
        <div class="circle-pop w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-oikos-green-light border-4 border-white shadow-md flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <span class="text-oikos-green font-extrabold text-sm">{{ stap.nr }}</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-oikos-dark mb-3">{{ stap.titel }}</h3>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">{{ stap.tekst }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== CONTACT ===== -->
<section id="contact" class="bg-oikos-dark" data-nav-bg="#3C3C3C" data-nav-theme="light">

  <!-- Groene top-balk met 2050-slogan -->
  <div class="bg-oikos-green py-10 md:py-14 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto fade-up">
      <span class="text-white/70 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3 block">Contact</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
        Jouw woning<br>klaar voor 2050?
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Donkere onderkant met vraag + 4 stats + 1 knop -->
  <div class="py-10 md:py-14 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start">

      <div class="fade-up flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-snug">
            Een vraag of een gebouw in gedachten?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Vertel ons over het gebouw, de situatie en de ambitie. Dan kijken we samen wat er mogelijk is.
